songs.title: Chance The Rapper Vibin With Einer Bankz At Coachella

Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
(Mm) Yeah, yeah
Yah (yah)

Lazy male
Complainin' 'bout how high school he could
But his ACL
Aye, [?]
You're my daddy, how

Boy, get your big
Grown ass on
